1
00:00:09,114 --> 00:00:13,160
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

2
00:00:13,160 --> 00:00:17,800
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

3
00:00:17,800 --> 00:00:22,840
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

4
00:00:22,840 --> 00:00:28,000
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

5
00:00:28,000 --> 00:00:32,415
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

6
00:00:32,415 --> 00:00:37,167
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

7
00:00:37,167 --> 00:00:42,400
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

8
00:00:42,400 --> 00:00:47,853
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪

9
00:00:50,820 --> 00:00:55,760
=Rise Again=

10
00:00:56,144 --> 00:00:58,878
=Episode 8=

11
00:01:00,960 --> 00:01:02,600
Come back with me obediently.

12
00:01:03,079 --> 00:01:03,880
Otherwise...

13
00:01:05,599 --> 00:01:06,200
Mr. Gu.

14
00:01:08,319 --> 00:01:09,560
You're pushing your luck.

15
00:01:09,560 --> 00:01:10,439
Stop it.

16
00:01:15,040 --> 00:01:17,319
Su Wubing! How dare you
be rude to Mr. Gu!

17
00:01:18,760 --> 00:01:19,280
Su...

18
00:01:20,079 --> 00:01:20,959
Su Wubing!

19
00:01:27,879 --> 00:01:28,480
Are you alright?

20
00:01:29,959 --> 00:01:30,359
I'm fine.

21
00:01:31,200 --> 00:01:33,200
Did you kneel down
and beg the master for mercy?

22
00:01:33,680 --> 00:01:34,640
So he spared your life.

23
00:01:36,719 --> 00:01:39,159
The guy in the teahouse
was someone you hired?

24
00:01:39,680 --> 00:01:40,599
How shameless.

25
00:01:43,519 --> 00:01:44,560
So what?

26
00:01:44,920 --> 00:01:48,239
No one can stand in the way
of our family.

27
00:01:48,879 --> 00:01:50,319
If you refuse this marriage,

28
00:01:51,799 --> 00:01:53,640
your family will be
wiped out in Fan City.

29
00:01:54,359 --> 00:01:55,159
See them out.

30
00:01:56,040 --> 00:01:57,159
Again?

31
00:01:57,920 --> 00:01:58,719
You old fool.

32
00:01:59,840 --> 00:02:01,560
For Ningxue's sake.

33
00:02:01,799 --> 00:02:03,519
I was going to let you
live out your days in peace.

34
00:02:04,680 --> 00:02:06,000
You're digging your own grave.

35
00:02:07,319 --> 00:02:08,240
As for you,

36
00:02:09,120 --> 00:02:11,560
Su Wubing, once I deal
with the Lin family,

37
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:14,240
I'll make sure you watch
with your own eyes

38
00:02:14,800 --> 00:02:16,120
how I break her down.

39
00:02:20,560 --> 00:02:21,159
Mr. Gu!

40
00:02:30,879 --> 00:02:32,240
Let's call it a day.

41
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:33,719
I'll spare your life.

42
00:02:34,280 --> 00:02:35,080
Now get lost.

43
00:02:40,400 --> 00:02:42,280
Looks like he didn't survive by luck.

44
00:02:42,840 --> 00:02:45,840
Maybe his cultivation is already
above Xue Wuhen.

45
00:02:50,599 --> 00:02:52,960
Our score isn't settled yet.

46
00:02:54,759 --> 00:02:55,759
We'll see.

47
00:02:57,919 --> 00:02:58,520
Mr. Gu.

48
00:02:58,960 --> 00:02:59,240
Hey...

49
00:03:17,159 --> 00:03:17,520
Please.

50
00:03:19,479 --> 00:03:21,639
Thanks for your help.

51
00:03:22,120 --> 00:03:23,319
If you had arrived a step later,

52
00:03:23,400 --> 00:03:25,000
who knows what that Gu brat

53
00:03:25,000 --> 00:03:26,039
would've done.

54
00:03:27,400 --> 00:03:28,400
You're welcome. Uncle Lin.

55
00:03:28,919 --> 00:03:29,800
I promised you

56
00:03:30,520 --> 00:03:31,919
I'd protect Ningxue properly.

57
00:03:33,840 --> 00:03:35,360
Wubing has saved us more than once.

58
00:03:35,560 --> 00:03:37,840
This is a great favor to us.

59
00:03:39,000 --> 00:03:43,159
When you restrained Gu Yuanbing,

60
00:03:43,439 --> 00:03:44,759
have you considered the consequences?

61
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:46,879
Dad.

62
00:03:47,360 --> 00:03:49,599
He didn't do anything wrong.

63
00:03:51,240 --> 00:03:52,879
When did I say he did?

64
00:03:54,360 --> 00:03:56,759
I'm saying, to outsiders,

65
00:03:56,840 --> 00:03:58,719
you're already tied to the Lin family.

66
00:03:59,039 --> 00:04:01,120
From now on, you must be extra careful.

67
00:04:05,520 --> 00:04:06,080
Uncle Lin,

68
00:04:07,400 --> 00:04:08,840
I suspect your illness

69
00:04:09,319 --> 00:04:10,560
didn't come out of nowhere.

70
00:04:23,959 --> 00:04:25,040
(Personal Information: Su Wubing)
Xue Wuhen is trash.

71
00:04:25,639 --> 00:04:27,000
And so are you!

72
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:32,600
You can't even figure out Su Wubing.

73
00:04:35,879 --> 00:04:36,920
You still dare to stand?

74
00:04:39,279 --> 00:04:41,480
The villa where Su's mother lives

75
00:04:42,040 --> 00:04:43,560
seems to be a restriction set up.

76
00:04:43,879 --> 00:04:45,560
Our men can't get close.

77
00:04:48,360 --> 00:04:49,639
Tell Lin Hai to make his move.

78
00:04:50,000 --> 00:04:52,519
Get the Lin family's secret formula
within three days.

79
00:04:53,000 --> 00:04:53,600
Yes.

80
00:04:54,600 --> 00:04:55,800
And that Xue Wuhen...

81
00:04:56,240 --> 00:04:58,160
Turn the place upside down and find him.

82
00:04:58,680 --> 00:05:01,079
He's making money off me? Not that easy.

83
00:05:01,759 --> 00:05:02,199
Understood.

84
00:05:03,240 --> 00:05:03,600
Get out.

85
00:05:11,959 --> 00:05:12,759
Ningxue,

86
00:05:13,720 --> 00:05:16,560
I don't feel safe recovering at home.

87
00:05:17,519 --> 00:05:20,120
My chest still hurts a bit.

88
00:05:21,560 --> 00:05:23,160
Let's stay in the hospital
for a few days.

89
00:05:23,360 --> 00:05:24,399
I'll recover better there.

90
00:05:25,480 --> 00:05:28,040
Alright, I'll arrange the admission
right away.

91
00:05:28,040 --> 00:05:29,000
I'll stay with you.

92
00:05:29,839 --> 00:05:30,319
Look,

93
00:05:31,000 --> 00:05:32,959
I'll go notify the hospital first.

94
00:05:33,199 --> 00:05:36,040
I can guarantee you won't
be disturbed there.

95
00:05:38,000 --> 00:05:39,759
Rong.

96
00:05:43,480 --> 00:05:44,000
Rong.

97
00:05:44,720 --> 00:05:46,319
Isn't it better to recover at home?

98
00:05:46,519 --> 00:05:47,759
Hospital is such a hassle.

99
00:05:48,279 --> 00:05:49,079
No.

100
00:05:49,720 --> 00:05:51,000
The hospital is safer.

101
00:05:51,759 --> 00:05:52,240
You should

102
00:05:52,839 --> 00:05:54,000
keep an eye on things here.

103
00:05:54,199 --> 00:05:55,319
Don't let anything go wrong.

104
00:05:55,879 --> 00:05:56,759
Don't worry.

105
00:05:58,240 --> 00:05:58,720
Let's go.

106
00:05:59,279 --> 00:05:59,600
Alright.

107
00:06:00,120 --> 00:06:00,639
Careful.

108
00:06:02,079 --> 00:06:03,000
Rong, take it slow.

109
00:06:37,160 --> 00:06:38,120
No barrier.

110
00:07:35,399 --> 00:07:36,040
Uncle Hai.

111
00:07:44,839 --> 00:07:45,199
Dad.

112
00:07:46,839 --> 00:07:48,360
You... you didn't go to the hospital?

113
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:51,319
I suspected you all along.

114
00:07:51,439 --> 00:07:54,360
We said that just to lure you out.

115
00:07:55,759 --> 00:07:57,560
I came here just to help you
pick something up

116
00:07:57,959 --> 00:07:59,199
in case you needed it at the hospital.

117
00:07:59,199 --> 00:08:00,360
Stop pretending.

118
00:08:01,519 --> 00:08:03,160
We've already found out

119
00:08:03,639 --> 00:08:04,800
you poisoned Uncle Lin's medicine.

120
00:08:05,560 --> 00:08:08,000
Uncle Hai... why would you do this?

121
00:08:08,399 --> 00:08:09,360
What do you know?!

122
00:08:11,079 --> 00:08:12,759
What can a little girl like you do?

123
00:08:13,839 --> 00:08:15,040
Business is a battlefield.

124
00:08:15,439 --> 00:08:17,639
Only joining forces with the Gu family
is our only way out.

125
00:08:17,639 --> 00:08:18,279
You!

126
00:08:19,240 --> 00:08:19,839
Someone!

127
00:08:20,560 --> 00:08:21,199
Don't come closer!

128
00:08:46,832 --> 00:08:50,935
♪I defy heaven, fate,
and so-called immortality♪

129
00:08:50,935 --> 00:08:55,655
♪At last you say
we've been apart too long♪

130
00:08:55,655 --> 00:09:00,535
♪Unwilling, unyielding, I won't let go♪

131
00:09:00,535 --> 00:09:05,655
♪With you, even a dried sea
learns to embrace a stream♪

132
00:09:05,655 --> 00:09:10,055
♪If heaven divides us, I'll reunite us,
with love as our vessel♪

133
00:09:10,055 --> 00:09:14,735
♪If it forbids it, I'll shatter
the absurd Heavenly Dao♪

134
00:09:14,735 --> 00:09:20,135
♪Even if countless stars
turn into my foes♪

135
00:09:20,135 --> 00:09:26,529
♪To grow old with you, we burn
through the end of the long night♪

